summary: The unique depth of the sky and the rich warm days and nights
descriptionHtml:
This contributes to the ENB Skyrim unique warmth of color.
The main advantages worth noting:
- Deep and rich, well-worked by the sky.
- Warm colors, which do not have enough cold Skyrim
- Say no to ENB abundance of brightness! In a carefully balanced brightness of the ENB.


If you like the sharpness and clarity of images, sacrificing the different effects - then the ENB is not for you.
In my ENB you will find a lot of effects to enhance the picture, but you will not find it disturbing effects of the game - such as auto-focus in the wrong places.
Despite the rather impressive number of different effects and enhancements, ENB little picky about the hardware of your PC. In my ENB was performed balancing performance and image quality.

by Spayro

If you want realism - you just look out the window, not the swing that ENB  XD
